Output area centroids

Source: R/data.R
od_data_centroids2.Rd

This dataset represents geographic centroids of Output Areas in Leeds, UK.

This dataset represents geographic centroids of Output Areas in Leeds, UK.

Note

The schema data can be (re-)generated using code in the data-raw directory.

The schema data can be (re-)generated using code in the data-raw directory.
